              <h1 class="page-title"><span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden">How to (im)prove mathematics</span>
</h1>
            
              
                      <a href="/content/list-by-author/Rachel+Thomas">Rachel Thomas</a>                <a class="plus-share-button" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top" title="Share this page!"
           data-title="How to (im)prove mathematics" data-url="https://plus.maths.org/how-improve-mathematics" data-description="Article from Plus">Share this page</a>
